viewData.name: Canon EOS Rebel T5i DSLR Camera with 18-55mm Lens
viewData.short_description: Buy Canon T5i DSLR EOS Rebel Camera with 18-55mm Lens features 18 MP APS-C CMOS Sensor, DIGIC 5 Image Processor.
viewData.long_description: The EOS Rebel T5i DSLR Camera with 18-55mm Lens from Canon is an APS-C format digital SLR camera with an 18MP CMOS sensor and the DIGIC 5 image processor. It is combined with the EF-S 18-55mm f/3.5-5.6 IS STM lens for an effective range of wide-angle to standard focal length.
